HEADWORD: Adequacy
<hw>Ad"e*qua*cy</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Adequate</er>.]</ety> <def>The state or quality of being adequate,
proportionate, or sufficient; a sufficiency for a particular purpose;
<as>as, the <ex>adequacy</ex> of supply to the
expenditure</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

